{
  "stem": "16930.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 498.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I guess there were so many applicants, and I guess a reduction in visas allowed by the United States, that there were long waiting lines and a lot of people never got out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By the time my parents got the visa, I think around 1941, the war had already been declared, and you couldn't go through regular channels anymore.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't go like through France or through Belgium or through England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The plan my parents had was they sent my sister and myself on what they call a kindertransport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "United Kingdom had issued visas for 10,000 Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we were-- from Germany and Austria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1939.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the plan my parents had was that these things were really pretty rough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Things were really very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they sent us on the kindertransport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, parents don't like to send small children away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they felt they had to to save our lives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the plan was hopefully that if they got their visa, they would then go to England, and on the way to America pick us up from England.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We really didn't think in those terms, just kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you don't think in adult terms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is it difficult, is it not difficult, what is the number system, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They moved us into, because you-- we had to move out of-- they wanted to concentrate Jews in certain neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A number of months.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't exactly know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A number of months, because I went to school there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the kids in that school-- this was a public school, but all the kids in that school the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they focused the Jews in certain neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know if at that time they already had in mind what was happening.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
